FBIS4-39249 "drsov109_d_94007" FBIS-SOV-94-109 Daily Report 4 Jun 1994 Regional Affairs Yeltsin Staff May Dismiss Chelyabinsk Oblast Head Yeltsin Staff May Dismiss Chelyabinsk Oblast Head PM0606154994 Moscow NOVAYA YEZHEDNEVNAYA GAZETA in Russian 4 Jun 94 p 1 PM0606154994 Moscow NOVAYA YEZHEDNEVNAYA GAZETA Russian BFN [Report from column based on RIA, POSTFACTUM, and INTERFAX materials: "Chelyabinsk Oblast Administration Head Not to President's Liking"] [Text] Yeltsin's apparatus is discussing the question of Mr. Solovyev's removal. The specific reasons are not yet being given, although it is reported that the administration head "has in recent months been a source of tension in the oblast in the spheres of both political and economic relations."
